Atụmatụ Ala Canada bú The Canadian Land Surface Scheme (CLASS) bụ atụmatụ parametrization nke ala màkà iji ya mee ihe na ụdị ihu igwe buru ibu
Ọ bụ ihe nlereanya ọkaibe, na-eji usoro nhazi nke anụ ahụ iji gosipụta ike na mmiri nke ahịhịa, snow na ala
A na-emepụta CLASS na ọrụ nyocha n'aka D
